<conjf>Lacquered</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Lacquering</conjf>.]</vmorph> <def>To cover with lacquer.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Lacquer'd</xex> chair.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Pope.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lacquerer</ent>⟦br⟧
